  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Donald Trump's reckless actions are making the world less safe and setting back global action on climate change.

When he comes to Britain, people will make their views known on these issues and show him we are a diverse and inclusive society.<a href="https://t.co/tsF3jBHw9t" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2017/dec/12/donald-trump-visit-to-uk-expected-in-new-year-says-us-ambassador" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2017/dec/12/donald-trump-visit-to-uk-expected-in-new-year-says-us-ambassador"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">theguardian.com/us-news/2017/d</span><span class="invisible">ec/12/donald-trump-visit-to-uk-expected-in-new-year-says-us-ambassador</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">One of the biggest economies in the EU has chosen to leave.  Yet there's no self reflection from the EU as to why this happened, &amp; how the EU can reform. Instead EU leaders Junker and Tusk seek to punish Britain, rather than address EU's growing unpopularity across the continent.<a href="https://t.co/Sel3vEA8uo" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/DylanAlexJones/status/922847767105589248" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/DylanAlexJones/status/922847767105589248"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/DylanAlexJones</span><span class="invisible">/status/922847767105589248</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">I support the <a href="/KeepRiverLawn" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="857956898494132224"><s>@</s><b>KeepRiverLawn</b></a> campaign for a proper public consultation before this beautiful part of Tonbridge is sold to developers.</p>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Dylan Jones Retweeted Jeremy Corbyn</p>
